---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CtaBanner from '../components/CtaBanner.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/url';
import heroSubSrc from '../assets/gallery/hero-sub.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | Biff Lewis Geomatics – Land Surveyors Cape Town"
  description="Learn about Biff Lewis Geomatics – 30+ years of professional land surveying experience in Cape Town and the Western Cape. SAGC registered. Precise, prompt, and professional."
>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <div class="page-hero">
    <img class="page-hero-photo" src={heroSubSrc.src} alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href={url('/')}>Home</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span aria-current="page">About Us</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>About Biff Lewis Geomatics</h1>
      <p>We sell services by listening to our client's needs — building on precision, ethics, and a can-do approach across Cape Town and the Western Cape.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-accent-bar"></div>

  <!-- COMPANY STORY -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="label">Our Story</span>
          <h3 id="story-heading">A Practice Built on Listening</h3>
          <p>Biff Lewis Geomatics was established with a clear philosophy: professional surveying begins with listening. We take time to understand each client's specific needs, define the problem correctly, and then apply the right expertise and tools to deliver results that stand up to scrutiny.</p>
          <p>Based in Observatory, Cape Town, we have grown into one of the Western Cape's leading land survey practices — serving a diverse range of clients from individual homeowners to municipalities, developers, engineers, and attorneys.</p>
          <p>Our approach has remained consistent throughout: maintain the highest ethical standards, invest in up-to-date equipment and software, develop our team through mentorship, and never compromise on accuracy. Every deliverable we issue carries our professional certification — and the responsibility that comes with it.</p>
          <p>We welcome complex challenges. If a project seems difficult, our answer is still "can do" — and we back that confidence with the expertise and tools to deliver.</p>
          <blockquote style="border-left:3px solid var(--red);padding:12px 18px;margin:24px 0;font-style:italic;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--mid);line-height:1.75;">"We will go to lengths to explain and share the details of job processes and their significance in maintaining or enhancing the value of your property."</blockquote>
          <div style="margin-top: 28px;">
            <a href={url('/contact')} class="btn btn--red">Talk to Us About Your Project</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="story-aside" aria-label="Biff Lewis Geomatics at a glance">
          <h4>Biff Lewis Geomatics at a Glance</h4>
          <div class="aside-stats">
            <div class="aside-stat"><div class="n">500+</div><div class="l">Projects Completed</div></div>
            <div class="aside-stat"><div class="n">30+</div><div class="l">Years Experience</div></div>
            <div class="aside-stat"><div class="n">200+</div><div class="l">Satisfied Clients</div></div>
            <div class="aside-stat"><div class="n">WC</div><div class="l">Western Cape Based</div></div>
          </div>
          <ul class="aside-list">
            <li class="aside-item"><span class="aside-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Observatory, Cape Town — centrally located</li>
            <li class="aside-item"><span class="aside-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>SAGC registered professional surveyors</li>
            <li class="aside-item"><span class="aside-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Modern total stations &amp; GPS/GNSS equipment</li>
            <li class="aside-item"><span class="aside-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Current CAD &amp; GIS software</li>
            <li class="aside-item"><span class="aside-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Ongoing staff training &amp; mentorship</li>
            <li class="aside-item"><span class="aside-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Ethical, transparent professional conduct</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="section section--alt" aria-labelledby="values-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Our Values</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="values-heading">What Drives Everything We Do</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Our professional values shape every project we take on — from the first conversation to the final certified report.</p>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="5"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="22"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"/><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Precision First</h3>
          <p>Accurate measurements are non-negotiable. We calibrate our equipment, verify our data, and never cut corners — because the consequences of inaccuracy in land surveying are real and lasting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ethical Conduct</h3>
          <p>We operate with full transparency and integrity. Our professional registrations require it — and our clients deserve it. Every report we produce reflects both our expertise and our professional integrity.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Prompt Response</h3>
          <p>Construction timelines don't wait. We understand the urgency of our clients' projects and consistently deliver fast turnaround times without compromising on quality.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Client-Centred</h3>
          <p>We listen before we act. Understanding a client's actual needs — not just the technical brief — leads to better proposals, better solutions, and better outcomes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Modern Methods</h3>
          <p>We invest continuously in the latest survey equipment and software — total stations, GPS/GNSS, CAD, and GIS tools — so our results always reflect current professional standards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 014 4v14a3 3 0 00-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 00-4 4v14a3 3 0 013-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Staff Development</h3>
          <p>Our team is our greatest asset. We invest in mentorship and ongoing training to ensure every member of the Biff Lewis Geomatics team performs to the highest professional standard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDENTIALS -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="cred-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Credentials &amp; Registration</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="cred-heading">Professional Standards You Can Rely On</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Our registrations, certifications, and working practices meet the highest standards demanded by South African geomatics legislation and professional bodies.</p>

      <ul class="cred-grid">
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>South African Geomatics Council (SAGC) Registered</h4>
            <p>Registered with the statutory body governing professional land surveyors in South Africa — a mandatory requirement for issuing legally recognised survey documents.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Professional Land Surveyor Certification</h4>
            <p>All survey work is executed and certified by a registered professional surveyor — giving clients, attorneys, and municipalities confidence in every deliverable.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Calibrated Survey Equipment</h4>
            <p>We use calibrated total stations, GPS/GNSS receivers, and survey-grade instruments — maintained and verified regularly to ensure measurement accuracy.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Current CAD &amp; GIS Software</h4>
            <p>All technical drawings, models, and mapping outputs are produced using industry-standard software to the latest specification requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>30+ Years of Western Cape Experience</h4>
            <p>Decades of operating across Cape Town and the broader Western Cape region has given us deep knowledge of local land tenure, municipal systems, and terrain challenges.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Ongoing Training &amp; Mentorship</h4>
            <p>We continuously invest in staff development, ensuring every team member is current with professional standards, legislation, and best practices.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Company Registration No: 2007/008401/21</h4>
            <p>Registered as an incorporated entity (Inc.) enabling employee equity participation and long-term continuity of the practice.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="cred-item">
          <div class="cred-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <h4>VAT Registration No: 4900204153</h4>
            <p>VAT registered with the South African Revenue Service.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW WE WORK -->
  <section class="section section--alt" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">How We Work</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="process-heading">From First Call to Final Report</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">A clear, structured process so you always know where your project stands.</p>
      <ol class="process-grid" aria-label="Our process steps">
        <li class="p-step">
          <div class="p-circle" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
          <h4>Briefing &amp; Proposal</h4>
          <p>We listen carefully to your needs, define the scope of work, and provide a clear written proposal with a fee estimate.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="p-step">
          <div class="p-circle" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
          <h4>Field Survey</h4>
          <p>Our team visits the site with calibrated equipment to collect all required measurements and spatial data.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="p-step">
          <div class="p-circle" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
          <h4>Data Processing</h4>
          <p>We process, verify, and format survey data to professional standards — including CAD drawings, reports, and models.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="p-step">
          <div class="p-circle" aria-hidden="true">4</div>
          <h4>Certified Delivery</h4>
          <p>You receive a professionally certified, signed deliverable ready for use in planning, legal, or construction processes.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO WE SERVE -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="clients-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Our Clients</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="clients-heading">Who We Work With</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We serve a wide range of clients across the Western Cape — from individual property owners to large municipal and development organisations.</p>
      <ul class="clients-wrap">
        {[
          'Property Owners', 'Property Developers', 'Architects',
          'Civil &amp; Structural Engineers', 'Attorneys &amp; Conveyancers',
          'Estate Agents', 'Construction Companies', 'Municipalities',
          'Utility Providers', 'Government Departments',
        ].map(name => (
          <li class="client-pill">
            <span class="client-pill-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <Fragment set:html={name} />
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CtaBanner
    heading="Ready to Work With Us?"
    body="Contact Biff Lewis Geomatics today — we'll listen to your needs and provide a clear, professional proposal."
    btn1={{ text: 'Get a Survey Quote', href: url('/contact') }}
    btn2={{ text: 'View Our Services',  href: url('/services') }}
  />

</Layout>

<style>
  .story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start; }
  .story-text h3 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .story-text p  { font-size: 15px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 18px; }

  .story-aside {
    background-color: var(--purple);
    background-image:
      repeating-radial-gradient(ellipse 400px 280px at 75% 30%, transparent 0, transparent 20px, var(--purple-line) 20px, var(--purple-line) 21px),
      repeating-radial-gradient(ellipse 240px 320px at 15% 75%, transparent 0, transparent 14px, var(--purple-line) 14px, var(--purple-line) 15px),
      linear-gradient(145deg, var(--purple-dark) 0%, var(--purple) 60%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 36px;
    color: var(--white);
    position: sticky;
    top: 90px;
  }
  .story-aside h4 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .aside-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .aside-stat .n { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; color: #e87070; }
  .aside-stat .l { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); margin-top: 2px; }
  .aside-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .aside-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 13.5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }
  .aside-dot  { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--red); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 22px; margin-top: 44px; }
  .value-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--red);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 28px;
  }
  .value-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--red-light); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .value-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; color: var(--red); }
  .value-card h3 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .value-card p  { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.65; }

  .cred-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 44px; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .cred-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
  }
  .cred-check {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--red);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .cred-check svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; color: white; }
  .cred-item h4  { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .cred-item p   { font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.55; }

  .process-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 44px; position: relative; list-style: none; padding: 0;
  }
  .process-grid::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 26px; left: 12%; right: 12%;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--grey-light);
  }
  .p-step { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .p-circle {
    width: 52px; height: 52px;
    background: var(--purple);
    color: #e87070;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border: 4px solid var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--charcoal);
  }
  .p-step h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .p-step p  { font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.6; }

  .clients-wrap { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin-top: 32px; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .client-pill {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-light);
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 9px 18px;
    font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .client-pill-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; background: var(--red); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    .story-aside { position: static; }
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .process-grid::before { display: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cred-grid   { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .aside-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
